author: nmalin
msg: error in parsing array in ajaxUpdateAreas, use a regexp tp split all parameters separate by comma and support this string a,{b,c,d},e as three parameters and not five. Patch related to OFBIZ-6496. Thanks Pierre Gaudin for this issue.
